<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Coinner - 암호화폐 허브</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <script src="/js/api.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="logo">Coinner</div>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/">홈</a></li>
                <li><a href="/auth/signup">회원가입</a></li>
                <li><a href="/auth/login">로그인</a></li>
                <li><a href="/support">고객센터</a></li>
                <li><a href="/board">게시판</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="hero">
            <h1>Coinner에 오신 것을 환영합니다</h1>
            <p>암호화폐 추적 및 커뮤니티 허브입니다.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- TradingView 비트코인 차트 위젯 -->
<section id="bitcoin-chart">
    <div class="tradingview-widget-container">
        <div id="tradingview_btc"></div>
        <script type="text/javascript" src="https://s3.tradingview.com/tv.js"></script>
        <script type="text/javascript">
            new TradingView.widget({
                "width": "100%",
                "height": 550,
                "symbol": "UPBIT:BTCKRW",
                "interval": "D",
                "timezone": "Asia/Seoul",
                "theme": "dark",
                "style": "1",
                "locale": "kr",
                "toolbar_bg": "#f1f3f6",
                "enable_publishing": false,
                "allow_symbol_change": true,
                "container_id": "tradingview_btc"
            });
        </script>
    </div>
</section>


        <section id="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h2><a href="/auth/signup">회원가입</a></h2>
                <p>회원으로 가입하여 좋아하는 암호화폐를 추적하고 커뮤니티에 참여하세요.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h2><a href="/support">고객센터</a></h2>
                <p>도움이 필요하신가요? 고객센터를 통해 문의하세요.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h2><a href="/board">게시판</a></h2>
                <p>자유롭게 의견을 나누고 다른 회원들의 글을 확인해보세요.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Coinner. 모든 권리 보유.</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>